{"tid":1431163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［極重要］全部撐深中淺黃絲既同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:16:32.000Z","uid":263821,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b99abfd76a04cbc7902c7e0bef985c609fbaa9","tid":1431163,"uid":263821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:29:56.000Z","msg":"好重要好重要好重要<br />\n<br />\n我朋友係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">課左好多金，發左好多次夢，食左好多T</span></span>G，但屋企人係黑警，所以住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">紀律部隊宿舍</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n尋晚佢同我講：<br />\n<br />\n「尋晚9點幾有人話有人被差佬拉左(我見唔到拉左),我估係抄id<br />\n到10點幾<br />\n我住個宿舍出面無lala開始有人圍有人大叫 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撩人出黎打交</span></span>，射laser<br />\n其實入面<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有老有細路</span></span> 有其他人係入面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢度只係民居<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入面好多小朋友</span></span>，有街坊話見到射到真係個窗白哂跟住瘋狂diu人大叫<br />\n<br />\n原來楝樓入面</span></span>嘅全部人都可以diu 都可以指罵<br />\n原來入面嘅同路人都係無value嘅<br />\n原來係真可以無差別嘅<br />\n點解要變到gum<br />\n(P.s無人dup任何野落樓)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">其實gum做同對準政權有咩好處？</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大佬入面唔只得差人，有小朋友，有同路人</span></span>，需要這樣嗎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">我中TG中到狂咳，我皮膚敏感 我住入面係原罪？ 同差佬咩人都打有咩分別</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要分化班死黑警，就要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">木馬屠城</span></span>，唔係令佢地同氣連枝，所以要令黑警屋企人撐我地，爭取得一個就一個啊！[/red][/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n即使有黑警抄牌，大家要撚狗，都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好分化黃絲，變相同黃絲割蓆</span></span>啊～～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不割蓆不分化不譴責<br />\n都要不破壞運動係同路人心中形象啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"125bc7eeee8608533e57293ea6c51db6a764954b","tid":1431163,"uid":799,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:30:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老味你唔識用字體大細同顏色就咪撚用啦"},{"pid":"60b6de2dab018236ca7094e0581e800f1de4a98b","tid":1431163,"uid":293257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"轉自FB 日月神教<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">有公務員宿舍住客好驚示威者搞到自己？嚮個窗度大大隻字貼返「光復香港 時代革命」，咁大家就唔會搞錯啦。禍必及妻兒係做硬，連最低消費都唔做，咁到時唔好怨。<br />\n<br />\n網友來圖，原來811港島東公海Tg Group其中一個Admin係住係柴灣公務員宿舍，即係有屋企人係警察，佢頭先響Group度鬧示威者之前點解去佢間屋示威，話點解要禍必及妻兒。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，就算你立場係支持示威者都好，你享受緊嘅如果係屋企人做壞事換嚟嘅福利，今時今日真係預咗要比人攪埋一份，呢個就係你享受呢啲人血福利嘅代價。<br />\n<br />\n鬼叫有屋企人係警察，最多就住就住盡量唔打中你，唔會停止禍必及警察妻兒。<br />\n<br />\n而家香港係打緊焦土戰，講到明焦土就個個人都會受影響，無呢個心理準備就唔好講革命。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%88%E7%A5%9E%E6%95%99-1064256847295827/?__tn__=kC-R&amp;eid=ARAEFCRt1GyiKhTKQqqFAdJtm5TlXStlKdui-Zmutp-OGVVToy_0mw9XcPeekrwZjTUCtRforuigJC_h&amp;hc_ref=ARRTkj-SDMoZo9Mg6bFCBEYhHyi4NIkLU3H5bG0_LrnIMpa99IhSBCmtn4IU37NcEBA&amp;fref=nf&amp;__xts__[0]=68.ARDehpMfzFiQFIiAPMCcOozI8Ec6TFw3EJxnouxy7CsvXluQdTTurYeAMTjdoePVFwRxIZbl6ZrRYoGjfBDEWjQbCyuxI3zQ2S9V5gohKr1bOH1tqvbmSoFXbNOkeLsTIiVUdmToaVcqwArXYyuxubjoYD1y5VAK_dXzZ8kOaVMGhbCJ_iLOZs8Y-sPQ5zsiyE0EShF6bbd6VpBxLrwSVjEyW9i0UZW6Y3B8sV6JcmG-MtsMEZDbG3ZcrETENDKvZ6I4x4D0WqO_ifyxsuNdH4Y0f4QFHu0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25A5%259E%25E6%2595%2599-1064256847295827%2F%3F__tn__%3DkC-R%26eid%3DARAEFCRt1GyiKhTKQqqFAdJtm5TlXStlKdui-Zmutp-OGVVToy_0mw9XcPeekrwZjTUCtRforuigJC_h%26hc_ref%3DARRTkj-SDMoZo9Mg6bFCBEYhHyi4NIkLU3H5bG0_LrnIMp